title: "Income Tax Calculator FY 2025-26 — New vs Old Regime (India)"
h1: "Income Tax Calculator (FY 2025-26)"
description: "Calculate income tax for FY 2025-26 (AY 2026-27) under both new and old regimes — with standard deduction, Section 87A rebate, surcharge, marginal relief and cess — and see which regime saves you more."
lede: "Enter your income once and see your tax under both the new and old regimes — including the ₹12 lakh rebate, standard deduction, surcharge and cess — with a clear verdict on which regime wins for you."
updated: 2026-07-13
